otoring/news/119115296/rare-locomotives-pulled-from-river-bank-in-northern-southland|title=Rare locomotive pulled from river bank in Northern Southland|work=Stuff|location=Fairfax|date=2020-01-29|accessdate=2020-02-18}}</ref>\n* '''January 31'''\n**{{Flagicon|Singapore}} \u2013 [[Thomson\u2013East Coast MRT line|Thomson\u2013East Coast MRT Line]] Stage 1 opened.<ref name=\"\u5c65\u52d8\">{{cite news|publisher=\u4e2d\u592e\u793e|title=\u4ea4\u901a\u90e828\u65e5\u5b9a\u74b0\u72c0\u7dda\u5c65\u52d8\u65e5 \u78ba\u5b9a\u7121\u6cd5\u5e74\u5e95\u901a\u8eca|url=https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201912235003.aspx|date=2019-12-23}}</ref>\n** {{flagicon|Taiwan}} \u2013 Opening of Taipei Metro [[Circular line (Taipei Metro)|Circular Line (First Section)]].<ref name=:01>{{cite web|url=https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202001215003.aspx|title=\u6377\u904b\u74b0\u72c0\u7dda 1\u670831\u65e5\u901a\u8eca|date=2020-01-21}}</ref>\n\n===February===\n*{{flagicon|Italy}} '''February 6''' \u2013 [[Livraga derailment]]: A [[Frecciarossa]] train derails at speed at Ospedaletto Lodigiano on the Milan\u2013Bologna line, killing two drivers and injuring 31 passengers.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/milan-train-crash-death-toll-injured-lodi-italy-a9320456.html|title=Milan train crash|work=[[The Independent]]|location=London|date=2020-02-06|accessdate=2020-02-06}}</ref>\n*{{flagicon|Hong Kong}} '''February 14''' \u2013 [[Tuen Ma line|Tuen Ma line phase 1]] opened.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e8%a6%81%e8%81%9e/article/20200118/s00001/1579285964085/%e5%b1%af%e9%a6%ac%e7%b7%9a%e4%b8%8b%e6%9c%88%e5%b1%80%e9%83%a8%e9%96%8b%e9%80%9a-%e8%a7%80%e5%a1%98%e7%b7%9a%e6%9b%b4%e8%bf%ab-%e6%b8%af%e9%90%b5%e7%a8%b1%e5%8a%a0%e7%8f%ad%e6%ac%a1%e4%bf%9d%e6%9a%a2%e9%a0%86-%e6%96%b0%e7%ab%99%e3%80%8c%e5%9b%a0%e7%a4%be%e6%9c%83%e6%83%85%e5%86%b5%e3%80%8d%e5%a2%9e%e4%bf%9d%e8%ad%b7|title=\u5c6f\u99ac\u7dda\u4e0b\u6708\u5c40\u90e8\u958b\u901a \u89c0\u5858