2-2013 season ([https://www.transfermarkt.co.uk/claudio-ramos/profil/spieler/155396]\n\n==Club career==\nBorn in [[Vila Nova de Paiva]], [[Viseu District]], Ramos played for [[Acad\u00e9mico de Viseu F.C.]] in his hometown as a youth before moving to [[Vit\u00f3ria S.C.]] in 2007. He never played a senior game for the team from [[Guimar\u00e3es]] and was loaned to [[Amarante F.C.]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.gmrtv.pt/atualidade/2155-oficial-vitoria-contrata-guarda-redes-assis-e-cede-o-ao-lousada|title=OFICIAL {{!}} Vit\u00f3ria contrata guarda-redes Assis e cede-o ao Lousada|trans-title=OFFICIAL {{!}} Vit\u00f3ria sign goalkeeper Assis and loan him to Lousada|publisher=Guimar\u00e3es TV|language=Portuguese|date=24 August 2010|accessdate=20 February 2020}}</ref> and [[C.D. Tondela]], who he joined permanently after winning promotion from the [[Portuguese Second Division|third division]] in the [[2011\u201312 Segunda Divis\u00e3o|2011\u201312 season]].<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.ojogo.pt/futebol/nao-profissional/noticias/interior/tondela-sobe-a-ii-liga-e-faz-historia-2583104.html|title=Tondela sobe \u00e0 II Liga e faz hist\u00f3ria|trans-title=Tondela promote to II League and make history|newspaper=[[O Jogo]]|language=Portuguese|date=3 June 2012|accessdate=4 March 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://desporto.sapo.pt/futebol/primeira-liga/artigos/claudio-ramos-renova-por-dois-anos-com-o-tondela|title=Cl\u00e1udio Ramos renova por dois anos com o Tondela|trans-title=Cl\u00e1udio Ramos renews with Tondela for two years|publisher=[[SAPO (company)|SAPO]]|language=Portuguese|date=11 June 2015|accessdate=4 March 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://observador.pt/2018/09/28/claudio-ramos-fez-o-que-quase-nunca-faz-e-decidiu-o-jogo/|title=Cl\u00e1udio Ramos fez o que quase nunca faz e decidiu o jogo|trans-title=Cl\u00e1udio Ramos did what he rarely ever does and decided the match|newspaper=Observador|first=Mariana|last=Fernandes|language=Portuguese|date=28 Sep