am, Devon|Northam]]: [[Devon]] ({{gbmappingsmall|SS4529}})\n*Noss Hill: [[Shetland Islands]] ({{gbmappingsmall|HU3613015575}})\n*Ottercops Moss: [[Otterburn, Northumberland]] ({{gbmappingsmall|NY944896}})\n*[[Pevensey]]: [[East Sussex]] ({{gbmappingsmall|TQ644073}})\n*[[Poling, West Sussex|Poling]]: [[West Sussex]] ({{gbmappingsmall|TQ043052}})<ref>{{cite PastScape |mnumber=1476574 |mname=Chain Home radar station CH08 |accessdate=9 February 2019}}</ref>\n*Port Mor: [[Tiree]], [[Argyll and Bute]] ({{gbmappingsmall|NL9442}})<ref>[http://www.users.zetnet.co.uk/mbriscoe/PAGES/PortMor.htm Pictures of Port Mor] {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20051104173025/http://www.users.zetnet.co.uk/mbriscoe/PAGES/PortMor.htm |date=4 November 2005 }}</ref>\n*[[Renscombe Down]]: [[Dorset]]\n*[[Rhuddlan]]: [[Denbighshire]], AMES No. 65 ({{gbmappingsmall|SJ012764}})\n*[[Ringstead, Dorset|Ringstead]]: [[Ringstead Bay]], [[Dorset]] ({{gbmappingsmall|SY751817}})\n*[[Rye, East Sussex|Rye]]: [[East Sussex]] ({{gbmappingsmall|TQ968232}})\n*[[St. Lawrence, Isle of Wight]]: [[Isle of Wight]] ({{gbmappingsmall|SZ530760}})<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.subbrit.org.uk/sb-sites/sites/s/st_lawrence_remote_reserve/index.shtml |title=St Lawrence |publisher=Subterranea Britannica |accessdate=10 February 2013}}</ref>\n*Saligo Bay: [[Islay]], [[Argyll and Bute]] ({{gbmappingsmall|NR2116066740}})\n*Sango: [[Durness]], [[Sutherland]] ({{gbmappingsmall|NC4170067500}})<ref>[http://www.users.zetnet.co.uk/mbriscoe/PAGES/Sango.htm Pictures of Sango] {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090803040515/http://www.users.zetnet.co.uk/mbriscoe/PAGES/Sango.htm |date=3 August 2009 }}</ref>\n*Saxmundham, [[Suffolk]], IP17 3QD ({{gbmappingsmall|TM411720}})\n*[[RAF Scarlett|Scarlett]]: [[Isle of Man]] ({{gbmappingsmall|SC2566}})<ref name=\"IoM_SubBrit\"/>\n*Schoolhill: Porthlethen, [[Aberdeenshire]] ({{gbmappingsmall|NO9086098180}}):<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.subbrit.org.uk/sb-sites/sites/s/schoolhill_chain_home/index.shtml |title=Schoolhill |publisher=Subterranea Britannica |date=29 June 2004 |accessdate=10 February 2013}}</ref>\n*[[Sennen]]: [[Cornwall]] ({{gbmappingsmall|SW376246}})\n*[[Skaw, Unst|Skaw]]: [[Unst]], [[Shetland Islands]] ({{gbmappingsmall|HP6634016805}})\n*[[Southbourne, Dorset|Southbourne]]: [[Dorset]] ({{gbmappingsmall|SZ1591}})\n*[[RAF Staxton Wold|Staxton Wold]]: [[North Yorkshire]] ({{gbmappingsmall|TA023778}})\n*[[RAF Stenigot|Stenigot]]: [[Louth, Lincolnshire]] ({{gbmappingsmall|TF256827}})\n*[[Stoke Holy Cross]]: [[Norfolk]] ({{gbmappingsmall|TG257028}})\n*Tannach: [[Wick, Highland|Wick]], [[Caithness]] ({{gbmappingsmall|ND3200046900}})\n*[[Blackpool Tower|Tower]]: [[Blackpool]], [[Lancashire]], AMES No. 64 ({{gbmappingsmall|SD306357}})\n*Trelanvean: [[Goonhilly Downs]], [[Cornwall]] ({{gbmappingsmall|SW762193}})\n*Trerew: [[Newquay]], [[Cornwall]] ({{gbmappingsmall|SW812585}})\n*[[Ventnor]]: [[Isle of Wight]] ({{gbmappingsmall|SZ568785}}):<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.subbrit.org.uk/sb-sites/sites/v/ventnor/index.shtml |title=Ventnor |publisher=Subterranea Britannica |accessdate=10 February 2013}}</ref>\n*[[Warren, Pembrokeshire|Warren]]: [[Pembrokeshire]] ({{gbmappingsmall|SR9397}})\n*[[West Beckham]], [[Norfolk]]\n*West Prawle: [[Devon]] ({{gbmappingsmall|SX771374}})\n*[[Westcliffe, Kent|Westcliffe]]: [[Kent]]\n*Whale Head: [[Sanday, Orkney|Sanday]], [[Orkney Islands]] ({{gbmappingsmall|HY7590546125}})\n*[[Worth Matravers]]: [[Swanage]], [[Dorset]] ({{gbmappingsmall|SY967777}})\n*[[Wylfa]]: [[Isle of Anglesey]], AMES No. 76 ({{gbmappingsmall|SH3522093385}})\n\n==See also==\n*[[History of radar]]\n*[[Acoustic mirror]]\n*[[Battle of the beams]]\n*[[British military history of World War II]]\n*[[Chain Home Low]]\n*[[Civilian Technical Corps]]\n*[[Ground-controlled interception]]\n*[[ROTOR]]\n*[[RAF Air Defence Radar Museum]]\n*[[Castles in the Sky (film)]]\n\n==Notes==\n{{notelist}}\n\n==References==\n\n===Citations===\n{{reflist